Be a Bud - wiser ! 
„Éª„Éª„Éª
LIGHTS CAMERA _________ !

Quarantining this year made us miss out on a lot of things but brought back the old memories too. The summer card games, favourite childhood snacks, going back to basics for every day routine. This movie is about how we go back to creating the same level of emotion and connection as we did in the good old times!
The flowers, blurred effects, cut to shots with a pinch of modern Croma settings allowing us to create the same impact through the films while keeping in mind the safety of everyone involved.
This movie is dedicated to all the filmmakers who never cease to amaze and take this bull called COVID by the norms and create amazing film content nevertheless.
Here's to all of us and it's our time to mix the new with the good old basics.

node.text:
Hello, 
I'm Vaishnavi! I'm the graphic designer at Orbiting.

I handle all the design projects at orbiting, ranging from critical discourse, to graphic design and social media templates. I divide my time between making art, listening to lo-fi music, overworking and fantasizing about cheese ü§§

Orbiting is a social media platform that has a very unique concept. I love how orbiting allows you to explore everything around you rather than keep you held with your mobile, scrolling. One of the best feature in orbiting according to me is the no screenshot policy. Orbiting is a very user safe environment.
.
.
.

node.text: Waht the government done was just absolutely disgusting!!! So people couldn't go see there dying family members in nursibg homes but then they do this!!! Its not on at all.
Waht the government done was just absolutely disgusting!!! So people couldn't go see there dying family members in nursibg homes but then they do this!!! Its not on at all.

Are we in this together or not?

I want to return to life as we knew what it was. I want to say to my girls ok let's do dinner Friday night. I want to say mom c'mon lets go to town and go shopping, i want to go see my nephews and nieces and hug them and hold them, i want to go give my auntie a hug, but i cant, because we have been told to practice social distancing. 

But its ok for our Government to attend a Golfing dinner with 80 people in attendance. Our Government are supposed to lead in example and teach us and show us whats right and whats wrong. I am confused. I am struggling. I want focus. I want to know what's right and wrong. What was so important and urgent for all of those 80 ppl to be in attendance together for? 

Why is there one rule for us and another for them?? 

Also I choose to wear a mask because i want to protect myself and others. That's my choice. I dont know if i have the virus, i dont know if you have it and you don't know my background just like I dont know yours. 

Please be kind and respectful of others.

Thanks again everyone who shopped my masks! All orders are packaged and ready to be sent tomorrow! Don't forget to adjust your elastics when you get them! See my video if you would like to know how. I still have a bunch of stock, so I won't be sewing any more masks for a little while.

node.text:
Bagi Anda yang memiliki pengalaman dan merupakan praktisi di bidang tertentu, pengetahuan teori dan implementasi praktis adalah hal yang Anda kuasai dan merupakan sumber daya dan pengetahuan yang dibutuhkan oleh pihak-pihak tertentu.
.
Jika Anda memiliki komunitas dan biasa berkumpul pada waktu tertentu, pasti akan terkendala dengan kondisi pandemi saat ini. 
.
Reuni konsep lama sudah pasti tidak bisa dilakukan.
.
Anda tidak leluasa bepergian luar kota.
.
Terbatas untuk kumpul-kumpul dan nongkrong untuk sharing.
Kami memungkinkan Anda untuk tetap berbagi pengetahuan kepada anggota komunitas Anda maupun masyarakat luas dengan mudah karena ilmu, informasi dan pengalaman adalah hal bermanfaat yang harus dibagikan.
.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by JASA DESINFEKTAN SAMARINDA on August 23, 2020. Image may contain: text that says 'GOOD KILLS. O WATCH VIDEO I'm Here!! LLABNC Jam Manggalas Warung manggala Ready to Kill the Viruses 5 Swipe Left'.

node.text:
Terima kasih kepada @warungmanggala.smd sudah mempercayakan kepada kami untuk disterilkan

GOOD KILLS memiliki berbagai Kelebihan , diantaranya :

1. Menggunakan Mesin khusus Interior dan Eksterior yang dibedakan.
2. Menggunakan Mesin Interior dengan Techno Ultrasonic Ocean 
3. Bahan Perabotan yg membutuhkan Sterilisasi secara Khusus,  kita menggunakan Hot Steam Cleaner.
4. Menggunakan Liquid Desinfektan yg Go-Green (Ramah Lingkungan dan Manusia)
5. Desinfektan GOOD KILLS  tidak bau seperti Fogging secara umum, namun beraromatherapy yang aman untuk Manusia.
6. Hasil Detail dan Tidak meninggalkan bekas pada permukaan yang di sterilkan. Tanpa noda.
7. Efektif membunuh Kuman, Virus dan Bakteri hanya hitungan detik, dikarenakan menggunakan mesin khusus.
8. Proses pengerjaan relatif cepat dan merata hingga seluruh bagian Rumah/Kantor.
9. Proses reservasi cepat dan siap datang kerumah sesuai jadwal yang disepakati (by Request). Terima beres dan bersih sehingga client tidak perlu repot.
10. Berpengalaman dan Terpercaya sudah berbagai jenis tempat yang menggunakan Jasa Kami, testimony dapat dilihat pada @goodkills.samarinda di highlight.

Dapatkan layanan kami dengan menghubungi admin @goodkills.samarinda .
PROTEKSI DIRI bisa menggunakan Masker, Handsanitizer, Multivitamin maupun penerapan Physical Distance.

PROTEKSI LINGKUNGAN satu2nya dengan sterilisasi dengan Desinfektan secara merata pada tempat tinggal/usaha Anda.

Jangan sampai #StayAtHome namun HOME kita tidak STERIL dan ter-PROTEKSI.

node.text: Yes, I struggled too. I didn’t have the right information and thankfully later I changed. It was so hard for me. Thank you for sharing üòò
Yes, I struggled too. I didn’t have the right information and thankfully later I changed. It was so hard for me. Thank you for sharing üòò

At 27 I found myself all alone, lost and in tears. I was leading a lifestyle that didn’t support me, I was always tired, stopped exercising as I should, I was eating unhealthy food and I just didn’t love myself enough. I honestly felt powerless to change.⁠

⁠

üò∂⁠

⁠

As a kid, I was introduced to personal development by my amazing dad @jucemayor Thank you dad üòò I love you for that and much more, you are always an inspiration..

üôè

and I was encouraged to play sports and eat healthily. But as I grew up, I forgot the importance of staying vigilant with my wellbeing...⁠

⁠

¬†üôä⁠

⁠

The problem with leading an unhealthy lifestyle, not staying active, eating mindfully and keeping your mental health in check is the result, you give your power away, you literally start looking for validation in others, you don’t love yourself enough, and you have no energy, you are always tired, unfocused and your mood is all over the place!⁠

⁠

üòé⁠

⁠

When you know who you are and what you want, it's a different game.⁠

⁠

ü§ì⁠

⁠

I went from being frustrated, lonely, powerless and unhealthy 

üòî TO

 feeling strong, confident, grateful, healthier and UNSTOPPABLE.⁠

⁠

üòä

⁠

Wellbeing is a continuous journey, you do not get there, you keep working on yourself because you are valuable and you matter.⁠

⁠

üëÄ⁠

⁠

Tell me, Did you struggle with your habits at some point in your life? How? ü§î ¬†It happens to the best of us…

Ôøº

#wellbeing  #socialdistancing #story #selfcare #selflove #frustrated #alone #depression #healthy #happy #raiseyourstandards #motivation #lifestyle #getfit

node.text: Burning the ole midnight oil trying to stay sane!  This one is 12x12 @liquitexofficial on canvas board.  Turned the world off today, so if you haven’t gotten a response from me, sorry, just went to paint land!! I have to tattoo you, so DM or text and let’s get your next project booked out!  Or, if you have work that needs finished, let’s get that booked and start finishing some stuff up!  I would LOVE to take on a few larger scale thigh pieces to work on throughout the winter!  I have some ideas, so if your interested in a big show piece from me DM and let’s talk about some stuff!  The more freedom I get the better the session price!  Willing to work with y’all to book some killer projects to keep me busy! Brilliant photo and love the mill stone : I recollect remnants of mining at Lathkill Dale on my last visit to the peak district : probably the best NP in the world üòä

I love the The Peak District; everywhere there are remnants of the balance or battle between man and nature. Yesterday, just above Chatsworth, we walked along the edge of a disused quarry and just at the end near this large standing rock, a large mill stone abandoned by the quarrymen and left for all time as evidence of his existence there. I just love it!

node.text:
Di era pandemi ini, kita tetap wajib waspada terhadap penyakit Demam Berdarah Dengue (DBD), lho! Karena DBD juga disebabkan oleh virus yang dibawa oleh nyamuk Aedes Aegypti yang dapat menyebabkan kematian.⁣
⁣
Agar terhindar dari penyakit DBD, sistem imun tubuh wajib ditingkatkan dengan mengkonsumsi makanan sehat kaya vit C dan antioksidan.¬†⁣
⁣
Yuk, simak di gambar, makanan sehat apa saja yang bisa meminimalisir risiko terkena DBD.⁣
⁣
Selain makanan sehat, pastikan kamu juga terlindungi dengan Asuransi Mikro Pelindungku. Yuk, temukan informasinya di sini bit.ly/asuransimikropelindungku⁣

node.text:
Old time haunting the moment.
This was in year 2019, where we took our steps to the unplanned mountains of Kholdai ridges, of Western Nepal.
The place is among the developing trekking trails definitely not for the beginner's.
We ascend up to the altitude of 4500m where lies the lake khayer. There is definitely more than the height we ascended for the one seeking thrill and adventures. 
Local claimed that few among their tribes seen another beautiful lake over the height and trail we stepped our foot. 
We descended down the lake to celebrate our joy of the fleet we just touched.

Definitely recommend those wishing for nice leg stretch with an adrenaline rush.

5 üåü üåü üåü‚≠ê üåü trek trail for me.

node.text:
#janamdin 

Shri Anant Padmanabhaswamy Temple - Thiru Anant Puram, Kerala

As it was my ‘Vardhanti’ yesterday (Birthday according to the Hindu calendar), ceremonies were conducted at home and several other places to mark the occasion. To all those who so kindly took out the time to wish me all good things in life - a heartfelt thanks!! ‚ù£Ô∏è

Even though the temple at Trivandrum has been closed to the public since March due to the Corona crisis, special prayers were offered yesterday for my wellbeing by the Travancore Royal Family. They made sure that the blessings of Lord Anant Padmanabha Swamy are there for me in abundance. 

I have been sent photos of the Nirmalya Prasad that was received after the poojas. They also very kindly included photos of the temple tower so that I could have a virtual darshan of this legendary shrine. The busy temple which is also acclaimed to be the richest in the world looks so peaceful in the absence of any crowds. A picture of absolute serenity...

Absolutely grateful to Padmanabha Sevini HH Gowri Lakshmi Bayi who personally supervised the proceedings yesterday. 

•
•
•
•
•

node.text:
cbdMD Chicago (Virtual) Triathlon: Secured.
¬∞
Swim: 0.59 km in 00:33:34
Bike: 24.37 km in 02:03:30
Run: 5.10 km in 00:54:01
¬∞
I now have a baseline for future triathlons.
¬∞
Things started out uneventful. Just got stung by jellyfish in the first 15 minutes of the swim, then nearly got run down by a truck merging onto the highway that was behind me. The headwind was shit coming up the hill, but I was thankful for it when my chain slipped off of the lowest gear and got caught between the cassette and the free hub. The 5k started out (meh!), then after the second kilometer both of my hamstrings decided that they needed to cramp simultaneously. (Stretch. Keep going.) About halfway through the third kilometer my quads were lead, so I ended up finishing out the remainder of the run walking.
¬∞
Grateful for @bri_the_pt and our kiddos for all their support and cheering me on. Seriously, Mrs. Childs…I couldn’t have done my first virtual triathlon without you and your watchful eye (especially with the swim).
¬∞

node.text:
Terima kasih kepada Bu Ani karna mempercayakan kepada goodkills 

GOOD KILLS memiliki berbagai Kelebihan , diantaranya :

1. Menggunakan Mesin khusus Interior dan Eksterior yang dibedakan.
2. Menggunakan Mesin Interior dengan Techno Ultrasonic Ocean 
3. Bahan Perabotan yg membutuhkan Sterilisasi secara Khusus,  kita menggunakan Hot Steam Cleaner.
4. Menggunakan Liquid Desinfektan yg Go-Green (Ramah Lingkungan dan Manusia)
5. Desinfektan GOOD KILLS  tidak bau seperti Fogging secara umum, namun beraromatherapy yang aman untuk Manusia.
6. Hasil Detail dan Tidak meninggalkan bekas pada permukaan yang di sterilkan. Tanpa noda.
7. Efektif membunuh Kuman, Virus dan Bakteri hanya hitungan detik, dikarenakan menggunakan mesin khusus.
8. Proses pengerjaan relatif cepat dan merata hingga seluruh bagian Rumah/Kantor.
9. Proses reservasi cepat dan siap datang kerumah sesuai jadwal yang disepakati (by Request). Terima beres dan bersih sehingga client tidak perlu repot.
10. Berpengalaman dan Terpercaya sudah berbagai jenis tempat yang menggunakan Jasa Kami, testimony dapat dilihat pada @goodkills.balikpapan di highlight.

Dapatkan layanan kami dengan menghubungi admin @goodkills.balikpapan .
PROTEKSI DIRI bisa menggunakan Masker, Handsanitizer, Multivitamin maupun penerapan Physical Distance.

PROTEKSI LINGKUNGAN satu2nya dengan sterilisasi dengan Desinfektan secara merata pada tempat tinggal/usaha Anda.

Jangan sampai #StayAtHome namun HOME kita tidak STERIL dan ter-PROTEKSI.

node.text: TL;DR but it’s an important insight into my current thought‚ùóÔ∏èI don’t like our new reality. Some days it makes me really sad. I never thought something like a virus could end up with life completely interrupted. Almost half a year has gone by and my life is on hold. I’m thankful for the health of my family and friends. The only place I go is to the chiropractor, each week for my back. This week I went with my dad and brother to his office to bring back his stuff (he brought it home while the office was being renovated, planned pre-corona). Immediately upon entering the office building, you are reminded to social distance. Two people getting off the elevator weren’t wearing masks. It is such a small gesture that goes a long way. Fuck you for not caring about others enough to wear a mask. I didn’t want to touch the door handles or elevator buttons. I’ve always been a germaphobe but now it’s like the x games of trying not to touch anything. For the 45 minutes we unloaded the car and rode the elevator, besides the masks, slightly stuffy building, foggy glasses...it felt weirdly normal. I had less anxiety than I thought about being out in public. Granted it was 9 pm and the floor was mainly empty. Did I use hand sanitizer on my elbow when it touched the door? YES. For me, the exposure of going out in person is very hard for me to justify. Yes, I’d love to mindlessly wander through Target, TJ Maxx, Ulta and Michael’s. But is it worth the risk and exposure to coronavirus? For me? Simply, no. That’s what online shopping is for. I am envious of everyone who can go out, go on their usual summer vacations and just not worry. For me, I worry every time I leave my bubble, my house. I’m tired of living this way, but I don’t want to risk getting my family sick. I know it will be a while before there’s a vaccine; I know that I will have to get comfortable with going out in public/places at some point. Coronavirus on top of anxiety is a LOT. The change is a challenge. I’m just trying to figure out where to go from here.

Live for the moments you can’t put into words. üìùü¶©ü¶ãüí´

üìç shot in the beautiful and aesthetic streets of Istanbul.

Sometimes wen I want to describe a memory or experience from my travels, I’m in loss for words. That’s why I say, you just have to experience it for yourself to understand the bliss of the moment. The bliss in understanding a new perspective, change in what you believe, overcoming fear, achieving a milestone, to getting life lessons from a cart vendor on a beach to surviving a night at an eerie airport. Everyone’s journey will be different, lessons will be different. Travel is much more than spending money on lavish stays! I hope soulful travel is what you get to experience ‚ô•Ô∏è

node.text:
#Sahabatbpbatam, Badan Usaha Fasilitas dan Lingkungan bersama Direktorat Pengamanan Aset Badan Pengusahaan (BP) Batam melakukan peninjauan Waduk Duriangkang pada Kamis (20/8/2020) pagi. 

Peninjauan dipimpin oleh Anggota Bidang Pengelolaan dan Kawasan Investasi BP Batam, Sudirman Saad, menggunakan perahu karet dengan mengitari Waduk Duriangkang, didampingi oleh Manager Air Baku, Hadjad Widagdo, Kasubdit Pengamanan Lingkungan dan Hutan, Tony Febri, beserta jajarannya. 

Waduk Duriangkang sendiri merupakan bendungan terbesar di Pulau Batam dengan luas daerah tangkapan air (DTA) lebih dari 7.000 hektar dan luas permukaan 1.200 hektar. 

Selain itu, Waduk Duriangkang juga menopang 70 persen kebutuhan air bersih di Kota Batam.

node.text:
Terima kasih banyak Villa Puncak Tidar sudah mempercayakan kepada kami untuk disterilkan

GOOD KILLS memiliki berbagai Kelebihan , diantaranya :

1. Menggunakan Mesin khusus Interior dan Eksterior yang dibedakan.
2. Menggunakan Mesin Interior dengan Techno Ultrasonic Ocean 
3. Bahan Perabotan yg membutuhkan Sterilisasi secara Khusus,  kita menggunakan Hot Steam Cleaner.
4. Menggunakan Liquid Desinfektan yg Go-Green (Ramah Lingkungan dan Manusia)
5. Desinfektan GOOD KILLS  tidak bau seperti Fogging secara umum, namun beraromatherapy yang aman untuk Manusia.
6. Hasil Detail dan Tidak meninggalkan bekas pada permukaan yang di sterilkan. Tanpa noda.
7. Efektif membunuh Kuman, Virus dan Bakteri hanya hitungan detik, dikarenakan menggunakan mesin khusus.
8. Proses pengerjaan relatif cepat dan merata hingga seluruh bagian Rumah/Kantor.
9. Proses reservasi cepat dan siap datang kerumah sesuai jadwal yang disepakati (by Request). Terima beres dan bersih sehingga client tidak perlu repot.
10. Berpengalaman dan Terpercaya sudah berbagai jenis tempat yang menggunakan Jasa Kami, testimony dapat dilihat pada @goodkills.malang di highlight.

Dapatkan layanan kami dengan menghubungi admin @goodkills.malang .
PROTEKSI DIRI bisa menggunakan Masker, Handsanitizer, Multivitamin maupun penerapan Physical Distance.

PROTEKSI LINGKUNGAN satu2nya dengan sterilisasi dengan Desinfektan secara merata pada tempat tinggal/usaha Anda.

Jangan sampai #StayAtHome namun HOME kita tidak STERIL dan ter-PROTEKSI.

Salah satu skincare yang wajib banget kamu punya adalah face mist. Selain bisa bikin makeup
tahan lama, face mist juga membuat wajahmu jauh lebih fresh dan mengunci kelembapan.

Harga face mist emang cukup mahal, tapi ternyata kalau kita bikin sendiri pasti bakalan lebih
hemat karena kamu hanya butuh 3 bahan aja!

Oiya, essential oil disini bisa kamu gunakan ataupun tidak. Gunakan face mist saat kamu merasa
kulit butuh hidrasi dan setelah menggunakan makeup.

node.text:
Raahon mein andhera hai 
Aaj anishchitao ne mujhe ghera hai
Kaha jaana hai maloom nahi 
Iss vidambana ne mujhe jhanjhoda hai 
Log kehte hai ye umar hi aesi hai, Sabke saath yahi hota hai
Iss bhool bhoolaiya ko hi zindagi bola hai 

Kehte hai ki lamho se zindagi banti hai 
Parr mein toh aaj bas daud rahe hai 
Lamho ko kaha sanjoh rahe hai 
Kal kya karenge ye soch rahe, aaj ko bas kho rahe hai 
Log kehte hai ye asliyat hai, sabke saath yahi hota hai 
iss bhool bhoolaita ko hi zindagi bola hai

Mein filmo mein jee rahe, khudko roz thoda kho rahe hu
Mein bheed chal rha hu, lakshay k kareeb toh nahi hu, fir mein kya karr raha hu 
Mein azaad toh hu, fir bhi samaj ki nazar se bandha hua hu 
Log kehte hai ye hi Jeevan hai, sabke saath yahi hota hai 
Iss bhool bhoolaiya ko hi zindagi bola hai 

Mein ab khudko samaj ki bediyon se azaad karta hu 
Unki soch se na mein darta hu, unke liye na mein jeeta hu
Aaj mein jeekar khush rehta hu, Lamhon ko mein sanjota hu 
Log kehte hai...... jaane do, ab toh bas mein khudki sunta hu
Roz khushi se mein zindagi ka abhivadan karta hu 
Ab mein roz zindagi jeeta hu 

Jus a writing, no connection ‚úåÔ∏è

Dame Joan Henrietta Collins, DBE (born 23 May 1933) is an English actress, author, and columnist. She made her stage debut at the age of nine, trained at the Royal Academy of Dramatic Art (RADA) in London, entered British films in 1951 and went to Hollywood under contract to 20th Century Fox in 1955. In 1981, she landed the role of #AlexisCarrington, the vengeful and scheming ex-wife of John Forsythe's character, in the 1980s prime time soap opera #Dynasty, which made her an international superstar and brought her a Golden Globe Award for Best Actress in 1982. In 2015, Collins was made a Dame by #QueenElizabeth II for services to charity. #joancollins

Video by Teuku Aufra Maretto in Fitness Embassy. Image may contain: one or more people. Beberapa hal yang bikin kamu ngga bisa-bisa handstand:

1. Latihannya cuma sekali-sekali, atau kalau lagi inget doang.

2. Udah jarang dilatih, sekalinya latihan, cuma asal coba-coba aja, kick up, jatuh, bangun, coba lagi. Gitu-gitu aja sampai sejam.

3. Ngga sabaran. Ngga mau mundur ke tembok dulu untuk bagusin entrance dan ngerapiin alignment, pemanasan juga ala kadarnya, ditambah lagi males stretching padahal tahu punya masalah dengan keterbatasan fleksibilitas.

4. Ngga divideoin. Jadinya ngga ada bahan untuk evaluasi.

5. Ngga belajar dari pengalaman. Udah sadar ada yang salah, bukannya evaluasi, tapi tetep aja dilakuin. Batu memang üòÖ

6. Ngga mau belajar untuk jatuh dengan aman (bail). Padahal ketika kamu udah bisa "bail" dengan baik, kamu akan jadi lebih pede dan progressmu jadi meningkat pesat.

7. Terlalu sibuk mikirin hal yang belum saatnya dipikirin. Contohnya, udah mikirin mau handstandnya lurus banget, tapi untuk nahan posisi freestanding handstand selama 10 detik aja belum mampu, kick upnya juga masih kadang dapat, kadang ngga.

8. Latihan kebanyakan dan selalu berat. Ujung-ujungnya pergelangan tangan, siku, atau bahunya cedera. Bukannya progress, malah harus istirahat dan ngga bisa latihan sampai sembuh.

Nah, dari 8 hal di atas, ada yang masih sering kamu lakukan? ü§≠

mungkin untuk sementara progress untuk LEAN EVERYDAY nya distop dulu, karena setelah diperhitungkan dan dipikir pikir mendingan BULKING dulu ajah ... rencana sih pengennya berat sampai 85kg atau 80kg sudah cukup ... jikalau dikasih lebih oleh Allah ya saya sangat amat bersyukur ‚ò∫

.

jalani aja dulu, kalo cocok ya skuy lanjut ke jenjang yang lebih serius (bulshit gaes kalo ada yang bilang gini, ini mah menolak secara halus ‚ò∫)

.

nah banyak yang nanya, bang lu kok sering begadang tapi olahraga lanjut trus, emangnya badan gak drop ? ... logikanya simple bro . asalkan cukup istirahat (8 jam sehari tidur, kalo saya tidur 6 jam sehari) ... alasan saya begadang karena JOKI MOBILE LEGENDS ‚ò∫ dan ngedit juga broh .. cape kerja tanpa team ... kecuali kalo projek besar pasti saya butuh bantuan kang @azisjs 

.

selain istirahat yang cukup, nutrisi juga harus tercukupi misalkan vitamin C sehari wajib 1000mg, protein sehari 80g, dan lainnya ... o iya AIR PUTIH sangat penting 2 liter biar darah bersih dan ginjal gak gangguan

dan pastinya saya pake suplemen ISOBLEND dan MASS MUSCLE GAINER dari @elitelabs.id ... pasti kalian mikirnya iklan ya ‚ò∫ .. padahal saya bercerita apa adanya ...

yaudah gitu aja ceritanya ... nanti dilanjut lagi yah kalo udah gemuk .. karena mungkin kedepannya badan ni ga akan keliatan SHREEDED lagi ‚ò∫ ... kemarilah dan berkumpulah wahai lemak baik üôè

Sri Mulyani menunjukkan kinerjanya masih memble lantaran pertumbuhan ekonomi kuartal II berada pada level minus 5,32 persen.
--
--
Namun, kemungkinan Sri Mulyani direshuflle sangat kecil karena Presiden Jokowi masih akan membutuhkannya.
--
--
Begitu kata Direktur Eksekutif Indonesia Political Review (IPR), Ujang Komarudin saat berbincang dengan¬†Kantor Berita Politik RMOL¬†sesaat lalu, Sabtu (22/8).
--
--
"Menteri-menteri yang kinerjanya memble, harusnya (Sri Mukyani) kena reshuffle karena ekonomi kita minus. Tapi secara politik SM (Sri Mulyani) aman, karena Jokowi masih butuh ke dia," kata Ujang Komarudin.
--
--
Selain Sri Mulyani, lanjut dosen Universitas Al-Azhar Indonesia ini, masih banyak menteri-menteri lain yang layak direshuflle karena masih menunjukkan kinerjanya yang memble. Antara lain; Menteri Kesehatan (Menkes) Terawan Agus Putranto, Mensos Juliari Batubara, Mendikbud Nadiem Makarim, Menkumham Yasonna Laoly.
--
--
Kemudian, Menteri Pariwisata dan Ekonomi Kreatif Wishnutama, hingga Menteri Koperasi dan UKM Teten Masduki.
--
--
"Menteri-menteri yang kinerjanya memble, harusnya kena reshuflle seperti Menkes, Mensos, Mendikbud, Menkumham, Menpar, Menkop dan UMKM," demikian Ujang Komarudin.
--
--
